{"tid":2341125,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米11系列將效仿蘋果取消隨機附贈充電器","createTime":"2020-12-26T05:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T19:34:49.000Z","uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"5a64276be825b977eac2d44036514615dd971117","tid":2341125,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2835000/2837838/MI-A6F92A9F-2BD1-4643-B0BA-76BBB04F8C69_1024_1024_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2835000%2F2837838%2FMI-A6F92A9F-2BD1-4643-B0BA-76BBB04F8C69_1024_1024_1024_1024.jpg&h=e7f7d557&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自蘋果（美：AAPL）iPhone12系列宣布取消隨機附送充電器後，又一家手機品牌效仿。小米 （01810） 12月28日新品發布會前，在其官方微博表示，小米11產品包裝中將取消隨機附送充電器，為「響應科技環保號召」。惟並未如蘋果一樣，連同取消附贈耳機。<br />\n<br />\n小米12月28日發佈會，詳情【下一頁】<br />\n<br />\n小米表示，現時每個人都有很多閒置充電器。不只是個人的困擾，也是環境的負擔。小米深知這一決定可能不被理解，甚至「吐槽」。在行業慣例和環境之間，是否有更好的解決方案？小米表示，將在12月28日的發布會上揭曉答案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2835000/2837838/xm_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2835000%2F2837838%2Fxm_1024.png&h=0087e039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n微博評論中，有網友擔憂小米手機配置高功率快充，支持私有協議，如果不使用專門配備的充電器很難達到最佳效果。如果用戶額外購買，又將承擔更多成本。<br />\n<br />\n另外，網傳三星計劃其即將推出的Galaxy S21系列設備，均不附帶電源適配器和耳機。"},{"pid":"07c32e6bd21b005b9c32c89a4ebe73633116841a","tid":2341125,"uid":295230,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T05:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無apple既料同名譽但要跟apple"},{"pid":"9e76ae2ebf8e297499d0d16abdae44ba89b91966","tid":2341125,"uid":91238,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T05:56:57.